The paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as part-of-speech tagging and dependency parsing, which are typically studied in the subfield of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The proposed approach uses neural networks, which are a popular tool in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) and recurrent neural networks (cs.NE) in related work.
